dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Roger Davis. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Elizabeth Torres.
Nice to meet you, Elizabeth! How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim for an incident that occurred last week.
Of course. Can you please provide me with the date and location of the incident?
The incident happened on the 3rd of November in downtown area.
Thank you, Elizabeth. Could you also provide me with the make and model of your vehicle involved in the incident?
Yes, it's a two zero one nine Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for the information. I will start the claim process. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Elizabeth?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help, Roger.
You're welcome, Elizabeth! Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
